ience)\\n\\u516c\\u53f8\\u540d\\u79f0: \\u672a\\u77e5\\n\\u5de5\\u4f5c\\u5730\\u70b9: Wall Street\\n\\u804c\\u4f4d\\u804c\\u8d23: Develop software for financial structured products that runs on Bloomberg terminals; Create tools for structured products for the Buy side and the sell side (CLOs and structured products); Develop middle office software for reporting and P&L; Provide APIs for developers in the buy side or sell side firms; Work in multiple projects at the same time; Develop software for a Financial Technology Software company that provides data and analytics and portfolio products for Credit and Structuring Traders\\n\\u804c\\u4f4d\\u8981\\u6c42: Must have Computer Science Undergrad / BS; Must have had an intensive background in programming either in school or at work employment; Must understand how to avoid Python memory leakage; Must understand garbage collection; Must understand how Python variables are saved in memory; Understand how to design an efficient parser; Skills required: PYTHON, JAVA; C++ is optional; Skills required: PYTHON, Java , C++, SQL, UNIX, database programming\\n\\u804c\\u4f4d\\u798f\\u5229: \\n\\u804c\\u4f4d\\u63cf\\u8ff0\\u603b\\u7ed3: Junior Level Software Developer position at a financial technology company on Wall Street. Requires a Computer Science degree and intensive programming background. Primary skills needed are Python, Java, and C++. Responsibilities include developing Bloomberg terminal software, structured products tools, middle office reporting, and APIs. Financial product knowledge is optional. Competitive compensation offered.\\n\\n\\n-------------------------\\nRank 3:\\nJD Content: \\u804c\\u4f4d\\u540d\\u79f0: Backend Software Developer\\n\\u516c\\u53f8\\u540d\\u79f0: CyberCoders\\n\\u5de5\\u4f5c\\u5730\\u70b9: Washington D.C.\\n\\u804c\\u4f4d\\u804c\\u8d23: Developing new features; Implementing a microservices-based architecture; Providing operational support; Maintaining and developing Drupal custom modules; Enhancing HubSpot CRM integration (API)\\n\\u804c\\u4f4d\\u8981\\u6c42: Experience building and maintaining RESTful APIs; Strong Object Oriented Programming skills; At least 3 years of experience with implementing RESTful APIs using PHP, Python, or Go; Ability to write complex SQL queries for MariaDB or PostgreSQL; Hands-on experience with AWS development using EC2, EB, IAM, S3, Lambda, Cloudfront; Experience with messaging frameworks such as RabbitMQ, Redis; Experience in Test Driven Development; Ability to set up and configure Continuous Integration environment; Knowledge of Agile practices\\n\\u804c\\u4f4d\\u798f\\u5229: $100,000-$130,000 Base Salary; Vacation/PTO; Medical; Dental; Vision; Opportunity to build a market leading service; Grow professionally with the company\\n\\u804c\\u4f4d\\u63cf\\u8ff0\\u603b\\u7ed3: CyberCoders is seeking a Backend Software Developer to join their rapidly growing ratings and reviews platform in Washington D.C. The role involves developing new features, implementing microservices architecture, and providing operational support. Candidates need strong backend development skills with experience in RESTful APIs, AWS, and database management. The position offers competitive compensation and benefits, with a salary range of $100,000-$130,000, plus opportunities for professional growth in a dynamic startup environment.\\n\\n\\n-------------------------\\n\", \"context\": null, \"expected_output\": null, \"hyperparameters\": null, \"input\": \"\\u59d3\\u540d: \\u672a\\u77e5\\n\\u5e74\\u9f84: 36\\n\\u6559\\u80b2\\u80cc\\u666f: bachelor: Bachelor's degree in Software Engineering (Mykolaiv Building College, 2011-2019); bootcamp: Ethereum Blockchain Developer Bootcamp (Mykolaiv Building College, 2022)\\n\\u5de5\\u4f5c\\u7ecf\\u9a8c: Senior .NET Engineer (04/2022 - 07/2022): Designed and developed an educational application for teachers and students using .NET Core, Angular 13, and MongoDB.; .NET Team Lead/Tech Lead (08/2021 - 07/2022): Led ba